All corners are “PS” Cyl. Conc. Mons. 15×40 cm/ Bearing True: Date of Original Survey, November 12 to December 22, 1987, and approved on September 12, 1990 and the survey duly executed by Geodetic Engineer Antonio Galang.

The tract of land herein reserved shall be non-alienable and shall not be subject to occupation, entry, sale, lease, or other mode of disposition until again declared alienable through Proclamation by the President.

IN WITNESS WHEREOF, I have hereunto set my hand and caused the seal of the Republic of the Philippines to be affixed.

Done in the City of Manila, this 28th day of July, in the year of our Lord, Two Thousand and Five.

(Sgd.) GLORIA MACAPAGAL-ARROYO

By the President: (Sgd.) EDUARDO R. ERMITA Executive Secretary

